</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unuppin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nuppin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(10/21/01 7:57:40 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sowing/Porting/Buffing for donations</span><hr size=1> &quot;I can't port yet...need 4 more lvls, but I know that that is the real money maker for us druids...nothing else will get you pp quicker&quot;<br>
<br>
at 29 porting is the best pp but there are many things at higher lvls that will get you faster pp. <p>Baking: 158 (DIE Brownies!)
